Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:34.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto dievča...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.92,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,440)\fs37.5\fscy90\pos(1170,963)}Lekárska kancelária - Školská ošetrovňa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:38.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prijala všetky vedomia naraz, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:39.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:42.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kvôli mne.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:43.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:47.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako vodca si splnila svoju najdôležitejšiu povinnosť, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:49.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyviedla si Bojisko z veľkej krízy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:52.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A okrem toho by toto nikoho nenapadlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:56.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Že po celej Guilde boli tajne rozmiestené klony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bol to Kanadin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bol to plán bezcitnej Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, vlastne... je to aj tak Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemala si na výber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:13.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som rada, že to hovoríš takto, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:24.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hej...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nie sú tu žiadne nemocnice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikto neochorie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nepovedala si to práve ty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tak prečo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:32.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prečo sa nezobudíš?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dopekla so všetkým!{\i0}
