Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ešte sa to nikdy nestalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:47.61,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,440)\fs42\pos(1215,970.5)}Anti-anjelska operačná centrála
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V takomto stave sme Anjela ešte nikdy nevideli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vzhľadom na okolnosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,je možné, že už sa nikdy nezobudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Samo o sebe je to nepravdepodobné.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:55.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zobudí sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:59.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakoniec sa zobudí a bude vyzerať, akoby len príliš dlho spala.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A keď ten čas nastane...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ktorou z nich bude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Shiina prehovorila!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:08.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto musí byť neskutočne dôležitý problém!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:10.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to problém.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže, ktorou Anjelom bude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tou prvou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tou, s ktorou sme šli na ryby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:22.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale tí, čo na nás útočili, boli krutí a nemilosrdní.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:25.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, a bolo ich asi zo sto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:28.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otázkou je, či stratila svoju vlastnú vôľu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:33.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pravdepodobne sa jej všetky vedomia natlačili do tej malej hlavy a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:37.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takto... všetko to tam pletú a robia tam hrozné veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:42.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže ak sa zabudí, tak je možné, že bude mať naraz 100 rôznych vedomí?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:47.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Štatisticky povedané, šanca, že sa zobudí ako dobrá Anjel, je asi 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo budeme robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S niečím už som začala.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poslala som Takeyamu-kun na územie Anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A s ním pár členov, čo môžu pomôcť s prekladom manuálu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo tak TK a Matsushita?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sú na ošetrovni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:01.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Držia hliadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:05.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,TK síce vyzerá tak, ale jeho angličtina stojí za prd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:08.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vymažete všetky dáta a zmeníte heslo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:12.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a tým zapečatíte jej schopnosti.  Mám pravdu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale to bude fungovať len ako dočasné opatrenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozumieš tomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Časom získa prístup a začne znova vytvárať dáta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak to by sme proste mohli zničiť celý stroj, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V počítačovej učebni je spústa iných, čo môže použiť ako náhradu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Softvér tiež.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ach, sakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:34.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Páni, vyzeráte, že vám to dneska myslí trochu lepšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pojedli ste niečo divné?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jediné, čo môžeme robiť, je čakať na Božiu vôľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:45.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na koho strane asi Boh je?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meškám.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Test...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vydrž.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:47.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som trochu zoslabnutý.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Krváca ti čelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo vedomie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako sa cítiš?  Nie je ti nevoľno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som v poriadku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty si doktor alebo také niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie.  Len študent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Postavíš sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chyť sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V pohode?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej... vďaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je hrozné.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Musíme zavolať pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:40.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doriti!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:41.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nič?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idem pomôcť tým vovnútri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idem s tebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:47.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budeš v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trochu sa mi točí hlava, ale to nevadí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som Igarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:52.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pohnime si.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zachránia nás?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pohľadám východ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak sa dostanem von, zavolám pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak mám pravdu, určite sa vrátim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:49.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Požičiam si baterku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn!  Spoliehame na teba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Určite to prežijeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jasné!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to má byť?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bude to... trochu ťažké.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počúvajte všetci!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sme zablokovaní na oboch stranách!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mobily tiež nepomôžu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nijako sa nedá spojiť s vonkajškom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sme v tom všetci spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:24.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosím, nemyslite, že sa dokážete zachrániť sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:28.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zozbierajte jedlo a vodu a všetci si ju podelíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkaj chvíľu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto ťa postavil do vedenia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak kto by nás mal viesť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto sa postará o zranených?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tento chalan vie, čo robí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:42.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hádam nechcete povedať, že zranených necháme tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja... to som nemyslel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pomoc určite príde.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Len musíme dovtedy vydržať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spolupracujme!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak ste smädní, povedzte to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jedlo sa bude podávať v naplánovanom čase!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak sa necítite dobre, choďte za Otonashim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ešte chvíľu vydržte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak sa niečo stane, zavolajte ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:18.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:24.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo jedlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máme desiaty a nejaké drobnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:32.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na pitie máme asi 6 fliaš čaju a vody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To vydrží asi tri dni.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale vážne, si úžasný.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čím?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si veľmi starostlivý.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chcel si ísť do Afriky pomáhať deťom alebo čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:47.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie... To som nechcel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To bol vtip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neber ma vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:53.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, staraj sa aj trochu o seba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeš odpadnúť prvý.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:56.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Berie vodu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:02.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:05.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty hajzel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:08.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:09.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prestaňte!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Č-Čo chceš, vodca-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ideš ma zviazať?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rob si, čo chceš!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj tak nám nikto nepríde pomôcť!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:27.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Však?!  Všetci to viete, nie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To nie je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:29.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zachránia nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blbosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten chlapec nám minul spústu vody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To bola moja časť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odteraz už nebudem piť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak sa nebojte...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niekto mu tresnite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dovtedy sa neukľudním!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebojte sa, dostatočne ho potrestám.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:52.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to v poriadku.  Dáme si napoly moju časť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:55.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemáš za čo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn, poďme niečo urobiť s týmto chlapíkom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, vy tiež pomôžte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi.  Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niečo sa deje, poď sem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:21.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vráť sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vráť sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:57.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Od toho dňa... kvôli čomu som sa odvtedy snažil?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ona... Hatsune ma naučila o zmysle života.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A potom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Znova som videl, ako niekto predo mnou prišiel o život.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vôbec nič sa nezmenilo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Som stále bezmocný.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Odvtedy sa vôbec nič nezmenilo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:29.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakra!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemala by si si na chvíľu odpočinúť?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chcem ešte trochu čítať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No dobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu máš.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bolo by zlé, keby si sa nachladila.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:56.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stále neviem, prečo ti nie je lepšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno keby sa našiel darca...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darca?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:11.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Igarashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máš pero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jasné.
